title: Price index : Desktop and similar computers in Canada 2018
summary: The graph shows the Price index Desktop similar computers in Canada during 2018 .
The values are described using the ID 384 ( FPPI ) .
gold: This figure represents the Canadian price index of desktop and similar computers during 2018 . Maximum production is reached in the months of January and February at 962 . From then on production oscillates in a decreasing manner , plateauing at 959 during April and May and at 956 during June and July .
